annotations.title: The Royal Alaska - How to make better cocktails with Prosecco

textContent:
1 1/2  oz Gin
1/2 oz Yellow Chartreuse
1/4 oz Fino Sherry
2 Dashes Orange bitters
2 oz Dry sparkling wine (Prosecco, Cava or Champagne)
Lemon zest

Stir all but the wine
Strain into coupe
Top with wine and garnish with lemon twist
